snippet.title: Hannah King
snippet.description:
This channel is made for fans of the Canadian CBC tv show Heartland.  It doesn't matter if you have only seen one episode or if you have seen all 14 seasons, if you love Heartland I promise you will love this channel.   Not only will you be kept up to date with everything that is happening on the set of Heartland but you will also get a look at their lives off screen as I share the updates from the Heartland cast both on and off screen. Ever wondered what Amber Marshall is up to when she is not playing Amy Fleming? Amber Marshall's daily instagram updates will be posted on ths channel.

Excited for the upcoming season of Heartland? Lets discuss all the possibilities of what could happen in the new season of Heartland with new videos posted daily!
